reviewText: This was a good movie but seemed awfully long.

Cast wasted in slack suspense less anti Communist tripe. Anyone with even scant knowledge of the Second World War must dismiss this as low grade propaganda. There were a great many terrific movies made during the 1950's. This nasty piece of junk is not one of them.

nice little film i saw in my youth. the set up is soldier cum oss agent on trial for murder. his career is told in flashback via co stars cochran, malden, and thaxter, and others. nice little twist ending
